#. Tag: menuchoice
#: using-kturtle.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export to HTML...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Arkiv</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Exportera till HTML...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kturtle.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Exports the current content of the Editor as an &HTML; file that includes "
